Package: nhsbsa
Title: Access NHS Business Services Authority Open Data Portal API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("NHS Business Services Authority", , , "opendata@nhsbsa.net", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions to access and download data from the NHS Business 
    Services Authority (NHSBSA) Open Data Portal API. Includes functions to list 
    available datasets, retrieve metadata, and download prescribing and other 
    healthcare data.
